If you want the blob bigger
Change:

w-[118vw]
sm:w-[114vw]
lg:w-[108vw]
xl:w-[104vw]
Bigger values = bigger blob footprint.

Example:

w-[130vw] makes it much larger.

If you want it further right
Change:

translate-x-[10vw]
sm:translate-x-[11vw]
lg:translate-x-[12vw]
xl:translate-x-[13vw]
Bigger values = further right.

If you want it higher or lower
Change the outer wrapper:

top-24
sm:top-28
lg:top-24
Larger top value = lower on screen.

If you want the glow moved
Change:

left-[24%]
right-[-8%]
right-[4%]
top-[12%]
If you want softer/stronger glow
Change:

bg-[#d7b794]/20 → opacity
blur-3xl / blur-xl → blur amount